<TABLE CLASS="SPELLS" WIDTH=100%>
<TR><TH>Efficiency on DoT's.<BR>
<I><FONT SIZE=-1>Posted 1999-09-25 23:43:42 by Loper Thistlefoot</FONT></I></TH></TR>
<TR><TD>Your damage and effeciency for the dot does not take into consideration the fact that these spells take time to work.  Saying that a spell like this only does 34 damage and basing the stats on that are missleading.  Don't forget that there are 10 such ticks during the spells durration, for total damage of 340 pts for 140(ish) mana, makeing it VERY efficient indeed, instead of almost not at all.  We won't even talk about the DoT nerf, as I'm not sure what the % of gain for non-moving or loss for moving is...</TD></TR>
